    <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">Key findings</h2>
    <p class="muted" style="max-width: 46rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-5);">
      Respondents scored each risk on both how likely it is and how severely it would affect the
      Union. The results are mapped geographically and ranked by expected impact. An interactive
      version, the methodology, and the full annual report are published by the European Governance
      and Politics Programme at the EUI.
    </p>
